Tweaking LXDE desktop:

Center new windows:

paste just above next to last line of "~/.config/openbox/lubuntu-rc.xml" file

    <application type="normal">
      <position>
        <x>center</x>
        <y>center</y>
      </position>
    </application>

Add launchers to panel:

right click on existing app icon in panel and select "Application Launch bar Settings"


Select apps in right column and click "add"
then reposition with arrows if necessary.

Or add "App Launch Bar" to panel and then same as above.

************************************************************************************

Install "obconf" for more config options:  sudo pacman -S obconf

Install themes:  sudo pacman -S openbox-themes
